<package name="python-Timed-Threads" project="openSUSE:Factory">
  <title>Absolute time deadlines and thread cancelling for Python asynchronous threads</title>
  <description>A python module that adds the ability to set relative elapsed time deadlines on
asynchronous threads, and allows one thread to stop another by means of raising
an exception.

The main motivation of this module is to support TimedConstraint in the
open-source implementation of Mathematica, called Mathics3.</description>
  <url>https://github.com/Mathics3/python-timed-threads/</url>
</package>
